Where can I find a high-quality, printable Discord icon for an invitation?

You can find high-quality Discord icons on various websites such as Flaticon or Iconfinder. You can also visit the official Discord branding page (https://discord.com/branding) to download their assets, including print-ready logos and icons.

1. Go to Flaticon (https://www.flaticon.com/) and search for "Discord" in the search bar.
2. Explore the available icons and choose one that you like.
3. Click on the desired icon, then tap on "PNG" or "SVG" from the format options if you want a higher-resolution image.
4. Download your selected format.

For a print-ready logo:

1. Visit Discord's official Branding Guidelines website: https://discord.com/branding
2. Scroll down until you see "Download Assets."
3. Click 'Download' and wait until assets file is downloaded in zip format.
